{
  "page": "Galtry the Green",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Galtry_the_Green\" title=\"Galtry the Green\"><img alt=\"Galtry the Green.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/50px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/75px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/100px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Galtry the Green</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Galtry_the_Green\" title=\"Galtry the Green\"><img alt=\"Galtry the Green.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/50px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/75px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/100px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Galtry the Green TMK comic.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png/350px-Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png/525px-Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/48/Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png/700px-Galtry_the_Green_TMK_comic.png 2x\" /></a><div>Ser Galtry the Green, by Mike S. Miller</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgaltry.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgaltry.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Personal arms</span></th><td>\nNine jade mullets upon a field of leek green<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Galtry the Green</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galtry_the_Green&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Galtry <a href=\"/index.php/Hair_dye\" title=\"Hair dye\">dyed</a> his beard green in the fashion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a>. He owned a cloak made of a patchwork of many squares of fabric, each a different shade of green.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the lists, Galtry rode a white stallion with a green plume on his crinet that match the one on his helm. The <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greave\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Greave\">greaves</a> and gauntlets of his <a href=\"/index.php/Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Armor\">armor</a> had <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> inlay. His shield bore his personal arms of nine <a href=\"/index.php/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">jade</a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_(heraldry)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Star (heraldry)\">mullets</a> upon a leek-green field.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galtry_the_Green&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Galtry participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls\" title=\"Wedding tourney at Whitewalls\">wedding tourney at Whitewalls</a>. He faced Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">John the Fiddler</a> in his final joust, losing after ten tilts.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Galtry_the_Green&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafgaltry.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgaltry.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Galtry.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403150540\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.306 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 648/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10532/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7130/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argume